# рЯІСвАНрЯТї Fake Profiles вАФ Frontend Integration Guide

> **Base URL**: `/api/v1/admin/fake-profiles`
> **Auth**: All routes need Admin JWT token in `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header
> **Last Updated**: 17 Mar 2026

