## API Summary

| Method   | Endpoint               | Purpose                  |
|----------|------------------------|--------------------------|
| `GET`    | `/`                    | List all fake profiles (paginated, sortable, filterable). **Auto-filters `isFake: true` only**. |
| `POST`   | `/bulk-create`         | Bulk create fake profiles. Sets `isFake: true` automatically. |
| `PATCH`  | `/:id/toggle`          | Toggle active/deactivated. Errors if ID is a real user. |
| `DELETE` | `/:id`                 | Delete a single profile. Errors if ID is a real user.  |

---

## 1. GET /fake-profiles вАФ List All

> **Backend Logic Note:** You do NOT need to pass any parameter to hide real users. The backend automatically injects an `isFake: true` filter into the database query for this endpoint. Application's real profiles will **never** be exposed here.

### Query Parameters

| Param       | Type     | Default      | Allowed Values                                                                 | Description                     |
|-------------|----------|--------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------|
| `page`      | number   | `1`          | `вЙ• 1`                                                                          | Current page number             |
| `limit`     | number   | `10`         | `1 вАУ 100`                                                                      | Items per page                  |
| `gender`    | string   | `"all"`      | `men`, `women`, `non-binary`, `trans-man`, `trans-women`, `genderqueer`, `all` | Filter by gender                |
| `status`    | string   | `"all"`      | `active`, `deactivated`, `all`                                                 | Filter by account status        |
| `city`      | string   | `"all"`      | `Sydney`, `Melbourne`, `Brisbane`, `Perth`, `Adelaide`, `Gold Coast`, `Canberra`, `all` | Filter by city |
| `search`    | string   | вАФ            | Any string                                                                     | Search by nickname, email, phone |
| `batchId`   | string   | вАФ            | e.g. `batch_1710678900000`                                                     | Filter by creation batch        |
| `sortBy`    | string   | `"createdAt"` | `createdAt`, `nickname`, `gender`, `city`, `accountStatus`                     | Sort field                      |
| `sortOrder` | string   | `"desc"`     | `asc`, `desc`                                                                  | Sort direction                  |

### Example Request

```
GET /api/v1/admin/fake-profiles?page=1&limit=10&gender=women&city=Sydney&sortBy=nickname&sortOrder=asc&search=emma
```

### вЬЕ Success Response (200)

